{"level":"N4","levelName":"N4","levelNameCn":"基础","emoji":"🌿","quizzes":[{"id":"n4-q-001","type":"multiple-choice","topic":"grammar","question":"「天気予報によると、明日雨が降る___。」填入正确的语法。","emoji":"📝","options":[{"id":"a","text":"そうです","isCorrect":true},{"id":"b","text":"ようです","isCorrect":false},{"id":"c","text":"みたいです","isCorrect":false},{"id":"d","text":"でしょう","isCorrect":false}],"explanation":"传闻用「～そうです」。前面接「降る」（普通形）。「ようです」「みたいです」是推测，「でしょう」表示可能性。","sourceRef":"n4-g-001"},{"id":"n4-q-002","type":"multiple-choice","topic":"vocabulary","question":"「宿題」的读音是？","emoji":"🔊","options":[{"id":"a","text":"しゅくだい","isCorrect":true},{"id":"b","text":"しゅくたい","isCorrect":false},{"id":"c","text":"しゅうだい","isCorrect":false},{"id":"d","text":"じゅくだい","isCorrect":false}],"explanation":"「宿題」读作「しゅくだい」。注意清音「しゅ」不是浊音「じゅ」。","sourceRef":"n4-v-013"},{"id":"n4-q-003","type":"multiple-choice","topic":"grammar","question":"「日本語が話せる___なりました。」空白处应填入哪个表达？","emoji":"✍️","options":[{"id":"a","text":"ように","isCorrect":true},{"id":"b","text":"ことに","isCorrect":false},{"id":"c","text":"ために","isCorrect":false},{"id":"d","text":"そうに","isCorrect":false}],"explanation":"「～ようになる」表示状态变化（变得能够～）。前面接可能形「話せる」。B「ことになる」表示决定，C「ために」表示目的，D「そうに」表示样态。","sourceRef":"n4-g-002"},{"id":"n4-q-004","type":"multiple-choice","topic":"vocabulary","question":"「嬉しい」的意思是什么？","emoji":"💬","options":[{"id":"a","text":"高兴","isCorrect":true},{"id":"b","text":"悲伤","isCorrect":false},{"id":"c","text":"担心","isCorrect":false},{"id":"d","text":"愤怒","isCorrect":false}],"explanation":"「嬉しい（うれしい）」是表示高兴、开心的イ形容词。","sourceRef":"n4-v-020"},{"id":"n4-q-005","type":"multiple-choice","topic":"grammar","question":"「～てしまう」表达什么含义？","emoji":"📝","options":[{"id":"a","text":"动作完成或遗憾","isCorrect":true},{"id":"b","text":"请求对方做某事","isCorrect":false},{"id":"c","text":"正在进行","isCorrect":false},{"id":"d","text":"过去经历","isCorrect":false}],"explanation":"「～てしまう」表示①动作完成 ②遗憾/后悔。口语常缩约为「ちゃう」。","sourceRef":"n4-g-003"}]}
